[00:26.10] This being human is a guest house
[00:34.42] Every morning a new arrival
[00:39.62] A joy, a depression, a meanness
[00:48.34] Some momentary awareness comes
[00:53.97] As an unexpected visitor
[01:04.00] Welcome and entertain them all!
[01:10.17] Be grateful for whoever comes
[01:15.57] Because each has been sent as a guide